| Where is ChatGPT's training data stored before training?          | In large-scale storage systems within data centers.                                          |
| Does ChatGPT keep all books and websites inside the model?        | No. The model learns patterns from the data rather than storing it as a searchable database. |
| Where is the learned knowledge stored?                            | In the neural network's parameters (weights).                                                |
